{"type": "article", "id": 14598, "title": "无刻度挂钟", "description": "", "date": "2015-09-08T06:59:34Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 22, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606000310OeYGLZ45inkhfyxD.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t钟表的存在往往是让人们清楚时间，但这位设计师显然不想这样做。一根指针，一个数字，和一个小时的区间范围，就是这面挂钟的全部。Sabrina Fossi 尽可能缩小时间的概念，只留一个小的参照，剩下一片空白供人们想象。对于分秒必争的人来说，这面钟显然并不合适。但也许，我们对时间的概念太过紧张，这一刻与下一刻的区别并不大，放松一点，重要的是对这片空白的描绘。挂钟有6种颜色，售价79欧。<a href=\"http://www.crowdyhouse.com/shop/freakishclock-wall-clock/\" target=\"_blank\">这里是购买链接。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142048eswpuI8c1rfn2liU.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"1034\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.95740741\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142048CUrXleLD3xFIBj4v.jpg\" width=\"940\" height=\"882\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.93829787\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142049dr0Lwn8oDeCf7Vgu.jpg\" width=\"940\" height=\"940\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}